sub_title: Customer Service Associate at LyondellBasell | Public Policy Enthusiast | Interdisciplinary Problem Solver | Tech Buff
summary: If there's a problem to be solved - I am up for a challenge. I have experience in various industries starting from foreign trade, going through gastronomy and customer service and finishing with esport and journalism. Thanks to this, I have learned that what truly matters is a team and the people you are surrounded with. I believe in the "work hard, play hard" mentality. I am a constant learner, open to feedback and encouraging growth in my teammates and myself.
